Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為果然還是被罵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像要吃了我似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我說「要離家出走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就說「有本事就走啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一句我一句的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…這玩意…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個我也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是有多想睡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走也頂不過幾天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校也不能不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好意思說這話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校啊 只要一回不去 以後會很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初倒是挺輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一整天不去 也不會有任何變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 因為不會變就日復一日地攢下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來自己已經徹底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 這種事還真輪不到我教育別人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海真厲害 家裡蹲不是白蹲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 宿海還是宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己夠嗆的時候 還總想著別人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣在意別人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是那樣 面麻比我更…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…我和雪集也談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直是活在面麻的陰影中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是面麻現在就在我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以…那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信面麻的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 不是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你買了牛肉咖喱哦 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉咖喱撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會 我只是來看日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的牛肉咖喱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完這個 也許就能知道面麻的願望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不瞭解的面麻 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的面麻的內心 就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:27.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩了 好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:36.12,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩了 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是好玩就是開心 只有這點差別
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本來就不擅長作文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有點不一樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩的時候摔了一跤 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這裡也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起去探望仁碳的媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.40,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病房入口 門診入口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我們經常一大堆人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的媽媽 一直都在住院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 給神寫封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫「請讓仁碳的媽媽快些好起來」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼弄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 是那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家決定一起製作煙火 我感覺好難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 說是把信裝進火箭煙火寄給神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 願望會不會就是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 一定是 那時候想做但沒成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞蛋仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要理什麼仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜吃東西 會變豬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變豬的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽拉麵 加了蛋花湯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有小健拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想餵你點東西吃 哄你開心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸差不多快回來了 快點吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 明天我也會去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你別跟過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你獎勵 張嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不能再做些奇怪的事情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 為什麼不去上學又穿著校服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嘛 穿什麼都是自由打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據火藥類管製法規定 使用煙火的火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須年滿18週歲 擁有國家資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具煙火一類的話 倒是勉強可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也需要許可證的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 正常想想煙火的確需要資格…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 昨天掃除的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集大量煙火 把火藥分別弄出集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞進廁紙芯裡面 但是會燒起來所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不明擺著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖 小鬼好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 以前我們卻認為這個可行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前弄成這樣 也真的以為它能飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為能做得比祭典上看到的更大 飛得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時還覺得高中生完全是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那年紀什麼都能做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺反而是那時候 我們什麼都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先想想辦法 找找大體的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.07,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「停」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 可不管怎麼想 這也沒戲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這麼多事 可如果不是你所說的面麻的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是無用功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 宿海君 你有好好向你那的面麻確認過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她本人確認 我可能是有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才一瞬間似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是先人一步的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和只能可憐巴巴望著他的雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 為什麼沒說出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是 要不是他召集大家去秘密基地的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 不是面麻提議的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對 我被面麻一個電話叫了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對 那天她好像有什麼事要商量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回想起來的 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻說過「集會的事情 不要告訴宿海」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.08,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7話 真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火？我認識會做的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們工地的一個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是祭典的時候會兼做煙火師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 仁太 想做煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想做來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 還有波波他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我去拜託他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳仁碳仁碳仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走不出空達爾城啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要嗎 我先幫你聯絡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事下次再說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 簡單的也要花這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是不能給你做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這麼多錢見都沒見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 總有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和安鳴去拚命打工 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 別擅自決定好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好嘛 這叫相互幫助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心啥 安鳴一週打七天工的話輕鬆搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊 我還沒說要幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡輸入金額知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是半舊貨的價格 這邊是新商品的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 然後在這裡輸入差額嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我花了1個月才掌握的技巧 你一上手就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這花的時間也太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面卻完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工倒是有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校那邊就請假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那不是不來上學的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 他們倆搞上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡~迎~光~臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺現在這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和小時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 給我膠布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿…海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海在打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火的事 他好像是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備怎麼辦 我們也來湊湊錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去陪宿海瘋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不參加的話我也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 要不要出來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上考試了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年級第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年級第二的某人在說什麼呢 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緊你的腳步 可是相當費力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 居然這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 絕對有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上倒頭就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清早飛快就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是今日小狗專欄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狗狗是母的 我就認定仁碳在做什麼奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗 奧斯卡爾醬 母 7歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴哥犬好可愛 這褶皺也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:55.39,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…向小客人們打招呼說歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.87,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托奧斯卡爾醬的福 客人增多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 那請在這名冊上簽個字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 仁太君退學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊…不過 為什麼這麼問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 問這種奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我最近看見他好像在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想仁太君有沒有把這些都告訴你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 不過我們家是自由主義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都由他自己去決定的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事有事有事 有事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波？嗯 我沒班 店長好像挺中意他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上他是和你一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 羊山的施工地？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一來就幹那個也太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯啦 賺錢的話還是體力活最快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭式煙火什麼的 花錢如流水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望…面麻的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多為自己想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這態度 讓人煩躁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 雪集和鶴子那邊有聯絡過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 倒是經常有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要是也來多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明挺擔心仁碳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 仁碳就是仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也這麼叫嗎 我叫他仁碳哪裡不對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 挺賣力的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 仁碳可帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在面麻沒有為自己想的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳卻一直在想著面麻的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心腳下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便動燈照的方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風能移動照明燈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥極了 閃閃發光的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥極了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多也得有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我媽做的味道好接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 仁碳 在學校辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺啊 意外地比總是宅在家裡要輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種活著的實感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是說實際上怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說一直以來我都太…那什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著感覺自己活著的仁碳 面麻也覺得自己活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們先把定金帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這些 能不能先開始製作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 不好意思 這事吹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心跟祭典的負責人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他罵說「居然幫高中生做這種事」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼拚命耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的負責人是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接和他談談去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本間家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 仁太君他們在為你做各種努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我啊 可是超和平Busters的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:32.77,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と夏の終わり 将来の夢 大きな希望 忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:39.61,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}10年後の8月 また出会えるのを信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:47.94,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}最高の思い出を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:56.30,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}出会いはふっとした瞬間 帰り道の交差点で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:22:02.02,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}声をかけてくれたね 「一緒に帰ろう」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}あぁ 花火が夜空 きれいに咲いて ちょっとセツナク
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}あぁ 風が時間とともに流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:10.43,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}嬉しくって 楽しくって 冒険もいろいろしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:17.19,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}二人の秘密の基地の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:24.57,ED-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と夏の終わり 将来の夢 大きな希望 忘れない
